    "an5.242:0.1": "Aṅguttara Nikāya 5.242 ",
    "an5.242:0.2": "25. Duccaritavagga ",
    "an5.242:0.3": "Paṭhamakāyaduccaritasutta ",
    "an5.242:1.1": "“Pañcime, bhikkhave, ādīnavā kāyaduccarite …pe… ānisaṁsā kāyasucarite …pe…. ",
    "an5.242:1.2": "Dutiyaṁ. "
  },
  "translation_text": {
