    "an5.242:0.2": "25. Bad Conduct ",
    "an5.242:0.3": "Bad Bodily Conduct (1st) ",
    "an5.242:1.1": "“Mendicants, there are these five drawbacks in bad bodily conduct … benefits in good bodily conduct …” "
